Interface AbstractCommand

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    AbsolutePathCommand, FileNameCommand, FolderNameCommand, NbEnfantCommand, PermissionCommand, TailleURLCommand
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbsolutePathCommandImpl, FileNameCommandImpl, FolderNameCommandImpl, NbEnfantCommandImpl, PermissionCommandImpl, TailleURLCommandImpl

    public interface AbstractCommand
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'Abstract Command'. Classe abstraite représentant une commande.

    The following features are supported:

    • Command Name
    • Result
    • Ressource

    See Also:
    TP2Package.getAbstractCommand()
